overview.en: Quantify Global is a one-stop quantitative trading platform for global digital currency, dedicated to building a global leading digital asset financial ecological environment of data, strategy and transaction.
overview.zh: Quantify Global是全球数字货币一站式量化交易平台，致力于构建全球领先的数据、策略、交易三位一体数字资产金融生态环境。
